835
01:04:09,240 --> 01:04:11,039
<font color="#ffff80"><i>Ayo kita berkencan sekarang.</i></font>

836
01:04:11,039 --> 01:04:12,879
<font color="#ffff80"><i>Aku benar-benar ingin berkencan sekarang.</i></font>

837
01:04:12,879 --> 01:04:13,879
